reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute Mini printer with Extra Rolls of Paper
reviews.reviewText: The boxes the printer comes in are pretty unassuming but the printer itself is very cute. It’s of decent quality and the cat logo on front is very cute. The paper that came inside the printer is not sticker paper but I assume the extra rolls the printer comes with is sticker paper however. The rolls themselves are not very large so I don’t think you get many prints per roll. Obviously this printer is mostly for fun and not like a production level printer but you can use it for crafting or journaling and scrapbooking. Very cute.
